      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just... it doesn't feel like life anymore. it's just like i'm a ghost living in a museum of everything we used to be. i try to do stuff, i try to eat or watch something, but i just feel like i'm waiting for something that's never coming back. everything is just gray. it feels like the world is just moving on without me and i don't even want to be part of it anymore.",
